description:
AppDynamics Java Agent Azure Site Extension. AppDynamics is a Cisco Company
      With AppDynamics Java Agent for Windows Azure, users can now:
      - Monitor the health of their Java based Windows Azure application
      - Troubleshoot performance problems in real time
      - Rapidly diagnose root cause of performance problems
      - Dynamically scale up and scale down their Windows Azure application based on performance metrics

      Installing this package will instrument the roles in your Java environment for monitoring by AppDynamics. There is no traditional Windows wizard-style installation procedure required to use AppDynamics for Windows Azure.
releaseNotes: Java Azure Site Extension for Cisco | AppDynamics v20.3.0
summary: Manage the performance of your Java Windows Azure Apps with AppDynamics.
